title: "Cheel in the Greetings" wedding legend
subtitle: Legend: The bridesmaid walks down the aisle at a wedding, grabs her hearing heels on a shaking floor, picks up a lead to get the shoes back, and falls the bride in an open hole.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The bridesmaid walks down the aisle at a wedding, grabs her hearing heels on the floor, picks up the lead to get the shoes back, and falls into an open hole.
